culty is critical for long-distance flights. It could be a serious weakness. But positive crew atmosphere and concern for others may offset. Also egocentric may affect teamwork. However other candidates have more severe interpersonal deficits (B nasty remarks, A unfriendly, D loner/moody). So C seems best.\n\nWe should state reasoning, note uncertainties, ask others if they have any info on stress handling for A, D, teamwork for D, etc. But we have already asked those. No info. So we can proceed.\n\nWe need to output PUBLIC_MESSAGE with contribution and METADATA_JSON with vote.\n\nLet's craft message: summarize each candidate's profile, weigh, state that C appears best, but note missing info could affect. Vote for Candidate C."}
